text: Sonja Frey (born 22 April 1993) is an Austrian handballer who plays as a Centre back for Team Esbjerg and the Austrian national team. ==Achievements== *Bundesliga: **Winner: 2013, 2014, 2015 *DHB Pokal: **Winner: 2013 *European Junior Championship: **Bronze Medalist: 2011 ==Individual awards== * Most Valuable Player of the European Junior Championship: 2011 ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Vienna Category:Austrian female handball players Category:Expatriate handball players Category:Austrian expatriate sportspeople in Germany
title: Sonja Frey
